<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>284</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 fù xìng diǎn rán zhōng guó de huǒ yàn zhǔ a wǒ men jìng bài nǐ
 zài yī cì qiāo xiǎng shì jì de zhōng shēng zhǔ a wàn guó jìng bài nǐ
 wǒ men de jìng bài qiān wàn rén de gē shēng dài lái tiān guó de zhù fú
 gěi yī qiè yuǎn fāng de rén yě gěi jìn chù de rén
 yuàn tā men dé tài yáng shài rè de měi guǒ yuè liàng yǎng chéng de bǎo wù
 yuàn tā men yī shēng yī shì dōu kàn dào sā lěng de hǎo chù
 shèng líng yǐ huàn qǐ téng fēi de xīn yuàn téng fēi de xīn yuàn
 zài yī cì diǎn rán fù xìng de huǒ yàn wèi zhōng guó zhù fú.</lyrics>
<title>fù xìng diǎn rán 迦南284</title>
</song>